gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 142, Grizzlies 105
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nuggets defeated the Grizzlies, 142-105. Nikola Jokic recorded 26 points (11-11 FGM), 14 rebounds, and 10 assists for the Nuggets, with Jamal Murray adding 23 points and nine assists in the victory. Desmond Bane tallied 23 points (3-5 3PM) and two assists for the Grizzlies in the defeat. The Nuggets improve to 23-10 in the regular season, while the Grizzlies fall to 10-20.
